metadata.description: Dave, Inc. engages in the development of a financial management mobile application to prevent bank overdrafts. It operates Dave, a financial platform that helps customers with banking, financial insights, overdraft protection, building credit, and finding side gigs. The company also provides Dave Banking, a spending account and debit card. Dave, Inc. was founded in 2017 and is based in Los Angeles, California.
